title: How to implement a custom Site Map in SharePoint - RapidFire
eventShortDescription: ​Description: Have you ever wanted to show consistent navigation elements for all Site collections but SharePoint out of the box does not let you?. Let us show you how you can solve this with the new features in ASP 2.0 and custom site maps. No code required, just configuration.
